<emphasis italics="true" pageId="147" pageNumber="148">Moussouri &amp; Tehrani</emphasis>
30693E mostly from Kashan) from 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus korolkowii" order="Solanales" pageId="147" pageNumber="148" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="korolkowii">
